{"tid":1666274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SHK Yoho疑似用木板封玻璃遮擋視野，方便狗狗佈署","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T06:39:20.000Z","uid":33729,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"040775016f485f497b2aac98973004306e21640e","tid":1666274,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家經過821、921元朗靜坐集會，都知道由元朗站去K出口就可以去到Yoho一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6mm2xi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6mm2xi.jpg&h=7580d9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於小弟喺Yoho返工日日都會經過嘅關係，發現呢幾日有工人開始裝木板圍封K出口至Yoho兩邊嘅玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8wVCATp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wVCATp.jpg&h=64ccf9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吸取過去兩個月嘅經驗，呢個位置兩邊嘅玻璃係非常方便觀察樓底有冇狗車同狗狗佈處，因為如果大家有細心留意，<span style=\"color: red;\">K出口旁邊其實仲有一個H出口，係一條樓梯可以直接由地下跑上黎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0PS9eL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0PS9eL.jpg&h=f9e2a014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當兩邊嘅玻璃被圍封，手足以至哨兵失去咗視野嘅優勢，喺元朗站/Yoho裡面集會嘅手足，就冇得再即時留意樓下有冇狗隻，萬一狗狗由H出口攻上黎，係一件極度危險嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在此提醒還望各位手足一切小心，毋忘721恐襲，祝各位今日武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b42cd8493af7c120848a91cc9ca161cdaf71b56","tid":1666274,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d986e42513f78c877e3d91dc2d13e55912630dab","tid":1666274,"uid":168057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90af7ba9cd7bbf452504d21a3c505ba0f46ca87e","tid":1666274,"uid":219308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:25:41.000Z","msg":"捱"},{"pid":"d940654944b870478a1410bc82158e4a61ad260f","tid":1666274,"uid":219308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90af7ba9cd7bbf452504d21a3c505ba0f46ca87e","tid":1666274,"uid":219308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:25:41.000Z","msg":"捱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46a67a2661e75b6dbd8fa0ed875f032b2c854da1","tid":1666274,"uid":219308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2e677d37d3e86c1eedbba90b9b7807f7d11efbee","tid":1666274,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:27:18.000Z","msg":"推 今晚靜坐活動風險異常高 <br />\n手足小心"},{"pid":"a2b46f8a6e94505b786f36c4368d08548357b804","tid":1666274,"uid":157037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1723993c79249383af1dbd7f927e4e31b9491560","tid":1666274,"uid":51171,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"可以係驚爆玻璃啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實係會阻礙視線，但唔好鳩屈人地個動機先"},{"pid":"8afc319b4a19d2a4d2c503d6dfae52f93bfadef0","tid":1666274,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"我估佢哋係驚俾人爆玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22389e245cc3f5a23802e751ffd5be0cbc410a6","tid":1666274,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"d43a3107bf422c5d144a847f7d5daeb73998cb7b","tid":1666274,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f403a9d686e03cf41ceb5a1d402aad5a3